  {
    icon: '🎯',
    title: 'Reaches Architecture-Focused Audiences',
    text: "Instagram's visual platform attracts architects, developers, and design-conscious clients. A DM from someone who has studied your exposed steel finishes and connection details is a pre-qualified lead who trusts your craftsmanship."
  },
  {
    icon: '📱',
    title: 'Handles Structural Photo DMs',
    text: "Builders DM photos of beam failures, corroded lintels, and structural openings — 'can you fix this?' The AI asks about the engineer's assessment, the beam specification, and the access, converting a visual query into a structured steelwork brief."
  },
  {
