const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What Instagram account type do I need?",
    answer: "Switch to a Business or Creator profile from your settings — a two-minute process at no cost, connected to your Facebook Business page. Structural steelwork companies producing fabrication and erection content gain professional analytics and audience tools that extend the reach of every crane lift video and workshop showcase across a broader contractor and developer audience."
  },
  {
    question: "What steelwork DMs come through Instagram?",
    answer: "Primarily architects, builders, and developers. Architects DM about exposed structural steel for commercial and residential projects. Builders ask about RSJ supply and installation for domestic renovations. Developers enquire about portal frame and mezzanine packages. Each sender has already viewed your fabrication and erection portfolio and has a specific steel requirement with a real programme in mind."
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly does the AI reply to steelwork DMs?",
    answer: "The response reaches the sender within seconds of their DM landing. Instagram read receipts confirm your steel company is actively engaged. Developers comparing three fabricator-erectors for a programme-critical frame — where every week of delay costs the project schedule — select the company that responds first with relevant structural questions."
  },
  {
    question: "What does Instagram DMs cost for steel firms?",
    answer: `Instagram DMs is £${pricing.addOn.price}/month as a channel add-on. Structural steelwork values span from £800 RSJ installations to £200,000 commercial frame contracts. One architect's exposed steel restaurant project, captured through a prompt midnight DM reply while two competitors' messages sat unread, transforms the monthly cost into the highest-return lead you convert all year.`
  },
  {
    question: "Can I reply to DMs personally?",
    answer: "Post a single reply into any DM thread and the conversation transfers to you for good. The AI recognises your message and steps aside. Most structural steelwork firms let the AI capture the opening scope — frame type, span, tonnage, execution class, and programme — then take over to discuss connection design, fabrication drawings, and commercial pricing."
  },
  {
